node.text:
The dream team… @kelseyleighdesignco, @thestagedlife, @mcgregorhomes and @emilyhartphoto show us how it’s done time and time again… but especially with this gorgeous living room. The design is so cool and effortless, the staging is so thoughtful and layered, the build is so meticulous and clean, and to top it all off… it’s shot oh so perfectly. And we’re loving every inch of it.
[Art: @manzilibyhuda]

node.text:
Happy Saturday!
Here’s a bit of a #vivirprojectmowry view to kick off the day. One of our favorite improvements we made to this space was adding that oversized picture window you see there in the back. Not only does it let in a ton of natural light, it also does a lot to blend the outdoors into the interior, which ultimately… brings us great joy!
.
